al training. Conclusions indicate that SR systems were extremely\nvulnerable under BIM, PGD, and CW attacks. Among the proposed pre-processing\ndefenses, PWG combined with randomized smoothing offers the most protection\nagainst the attacks, with accuracy averaging 93% compared to 52% in the\nundefended system and an absolute improvement >90% for BIM attacks with\n$L_\\infty>0.001$ and CW attack.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jan 2021 01:25:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2021 15:37:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-28"}
