ude the gender diverse as well as to include other forms of\ndiversity, I designed the ASTROMOVES project which is funded through a Marie\nCurie Individual Fellowship. Though slowed down by COVID-19, several interviews\nhave been conducted and some preliminary results will be presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2021 18:28:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
